dct_title_s: Erez-Israel, boundaries of the British Mandate. Israel 1:250,000 [cartographic material]. (North)
dct_description_sm: Israel. Agaf ha-medidot. Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Map shows historical sites, places of worship, towns, settlements, roads, political boundaries, and railways. North and South sheet. Complete. Survey of Israel. With additions of new settlements and roads to 1958. Road revision 1967.
